---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <Header slot="header" />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      About VSThunter
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-dark-200 leading-relaxed">
        VSThunter is a curated directory of the best VST plugins for music
        production. Whether you're a professional producer, a bedroom musician,
        or a sound designer, our goal is to help you discover high-quality
        plugins that inspire your creativity.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-dark-200 leading-relaxed">
        With thousands of plugins available, finding the right tools for your
        workflow can be overwhelming. VSThunter cuts through the noise by
        featuring only actively maintained, high-quality plugins across all
        categories — from synthesizers and effects to samplers and utility
        tools.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">What We Feature</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-dark-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-light mt-1">&#9679;</span>
          <span
            ><strong class="text-white">Synthesizers:</strong> Wavetable, analog modeling,
            FM, and virtual analog synths</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-light mt-1">&#9679;</span>
          <span
            ><strong class="text-white">Effects:</strong> Reverb, delay, distortion,
            modulation, and mastering tools</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-light mt-1">&#9679;</span>
          <span
            ><strong class="text-white">Samplers:</strong> Software samplers, romplers,
            and granular instruments</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-accent-light mt-1">&#9679;</span>
          <span
            ><strong class="text-white">Utilities:</strong> Meters, analyzers, MIDI
            tools, and workflow enhancers</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Plugin Standards</h2>
      <p class="text-dark-200 leading-relaxed">
        We list plugins in all major formats including VST3, VST2, AU, AAX,
        CLAP, and LV2. Our directory supports Windows, macOS, and Linux
        platforms, with cross-platform compatibility clearly indicated for each
        plugin.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-dark-200 leading-relaxed">
        VSThunter is an independent directory and is not affiliated with any of
        the plugin developers listed. We provide links to official download
        pages only. All trademarks and copyrights belong to their respective
        owners. Prices and availability are subject to change — always check the
        developer's website for the most current information.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
